text: Aditi Keshavdev Sharma (born 5 August 1996 at Jhansi) is an Uttar Pradeshi First-class cricket cricketer.Player's profile at EspncricinfoPlayer's profile at Cricketarchive She plays for Uttar Pradesh and Central Zone. She has played 1 First-class, 7 List A cricket and 10 Women's Twenty20 matches. She made her debut in major domestic cricket in a one-day match on 12 December 2014 against Hyderabad. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Uttar Pradesh women cricketers Category:Central Zone women cricketers Category:People from Jhansi Category:Living people
